title: Muscle Menus : Shakes, Bars and Smoothies
description:
For most bodybuilders and other strength athletes, we end up buying bland commercial energy, weight gain and meal replacement drinks. Not only are these often high in sugars and additives and extremely expensive, but having them day-in-day-out can become monotonous and boring. Why not make your own? Muscle Menus Shakes, Bars and Smoothies is packed with recipes for tasty shakes and mouth-watering smoothies which you can knock up easily at home.

Furthermore Muscle Menus Shakes, Bars and Smoothies has loads of great flapjacks, protein and energy bar recipes bursting with flavour and nutrition which can be quickly made helping you to obtain quick nutrition to reach your goals. Commercial nutrition bars are not only expensive but are often high in sugar and harmful trans fats, so why not save money and make your own tasty and healthy bars?

All ingredients are items which you can quickly purchase at your local supermarket or health food store. Some call for the inclusion of protein powders to bump up the protein content, some are based on food ingredients only
